                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/103346374/">Leohe</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">恋之极致，乃是心伤至死亦不形于颜色之忍恋也。相思便求得到，到底未有刻骨，沉挚之质到底也轻浅。一生自愿自使相思至死而不肯辞，乃恋之真意。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1198654810">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1198654810" class="vote-count">0</span>
