            <p class="comment-content">看三岛由纪夫讲他思想的来源和行动的准则。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1192628522">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1192628522" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1192628522" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1192628522">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tinghaitaotao/">无情与有情</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">#可重读#武士道入门选读，以及三岛的现代视角评析。是可以越读越厚一本薄书，对于理解三岛的生死观念和人生美学颇为重要。“武士道，乃求取死若归途之道。”这句话与西方流行的“向死而生”差别巨大，是绝不可混淆的。看过《叶隐闻书》和三岛其他几部作品后再来重读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1184757478">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1184757478" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1184757478" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1184757478">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
